summary: A new armor for rouge type characters. Inspired by Dishonored.
descriptionHtml:
Hello!
Here is a new armor mod. My first time messing around with textures and weight sliders.
The armor is available for both men and women.
Craftable - Upgradable
Weight sliders work.
No perk requirements to craft

If there are any problems please leave a comment. User Images are greatly appreciated

My other mods: 

Coats for Skyrim : https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/92852
